e%20I%20saw%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Epstein%20replies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20pal%20is%20a%20wonderful%20thing.%20Happy%20Birthday%20%E2%80%94%20and%20may%20every%20day%20be%20another%20wonderful%20secret%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20lawyers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-murdoch-wall-street-journal-lawsuit-docket-mystery-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edescribed%20the%20letter%20as%20%26quot%3Bnonexistent%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20defamation%20lawsuit%20against%20the%20Journal%20after%20it%20published%20its%20story%20in%20July.%20The%20Journal%20has%20stood%20by%20its%20reporting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20a%20representative%20for%20Trump's%20personal%20legal%20team%20directed%20Business%20Insider%20to%20a%20statement%20from%20White%20House%20spokesperson%20Karoline%20Leavitt%2C%20who%20described%20reporting%20about%20the%20letter%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bhatchet%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20I%20have%20said%20all%20along%2C%20it's%20very%20clear%20President%20Trump%20did%20not%20draw%20this%20picture%2C%20and%20he%20did%20not%20sign%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Leavitt%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frupert-murdoch-trump-health-updates-no-deposition-discovery-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump's%20lawsuit%20against%20The%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20ongoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222a63eab2-358c-4e66-bff5-19025258b2b2%5C%22%3ELes%20Wexner%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELes%20Wexner%2C%20the%20former%20CEO%20of%20Victoria's%20Secret%2C%20wrote%20a%20brief%20note%20to%20Epstein%20in%20honor%20of%20his%2050th%20birthday%2C%20the%20card%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20get%20you%20what%20you%20want%E2%80%A6%20so%20here%20it%20is%E2%80%A6%26quot%3B%20Wexner%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnderneath%20that%20text%20is%20an%20illustration%20of%20what%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20woman's%20breasts%2C%