3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20corner%20of%20Iowa%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20more%20than%20a%20little%20truth%20to%20the%20saying%20that%20it's%20hard%20to%20tell%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20girls%20and%20the%20hogs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20email%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Elkus%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20event%20he%20recalled%20in%20the%20birthday%20letter%20was%20%26quot%3Blong%20before%20any%20articles%20ever%20came%20out%20about%20Epstein%2C%20good%20or%20bad%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20reference%20to%20girls%20and%20hogs%20jokingly%20cited%20an%20%26quot%3Bold%20folk%20saying.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElkus%20recounted%20in%20his%20letter%20that%2C%20while%20visiting%20a%20local%20bookstore%2C%20%26quot%3Ba%20spectacular%20tall%20blonde%20woman%26quot%3B%20approached%20Epstein%2C%20who%20then%20%26quot%3Bdid%20his%20magic%2C%20and%20she%20ended%20up%20going%20home%20with%20him%20to%20New%20York%20for%20the%20weekend.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'll%20admit%20to%20wondering%20at%20the%20time%20whether%20Jeffrey%20somehow%20arranged%20the%20whole%20episode%20through%20some%20long-distance%20escort%20service%26quot%3B%20before%20being%20proven%20wrong%20after%20meeting%20the%20woman%20in%20Manhattan%20a%20week%20later%2C%20Elkus%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElkus%20wrote%20in%20his%20email%20to%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20story%20referenced%20in%20the%20letter%20was%20not%20meant%20to%20be%20viewed%20nefariously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20did%20not%20say%20that%20Epstein%20did%20anything%20inappropriate%20(and%20he%20didn't%20do%20anything%20inappropriate%20that%20I%20could%20see%20then%20or%20at%20any%20time%20before%20or%20after%20this%20incident)%2C%26quot%3B%20Elkus%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20a%20mature%20woman%20who%20was%20a%20sales%20rep%2C%20not%20a%20young%20student.%20I%20was%20highlighting%20his%20charisma.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221fd4262b-bb6f-4a49-a674-48d9273fb5d1%5C%22%3ENathan%20Myhrvold%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20many%20lewd%20entries%20was%20from%20Nathan%20Myhrvold%2C%20who%20was%20listed%20as%20a%20friend%20of%20Epstein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Myhrvold%20had%20retired%20from%20his%20role%20as%20Microsoft's%20chief%20technology%20officer%20and%20was%20working%20as%20the%20CEO%20of%20Intellectual%20Ventures%2C%20a%20firm%20that%20incubates%20and%20markets%20inventions.%20He%20would%20go%20on%20to%20found%20the%20global%20health%20organizations%20Global%20Good%20and%20the%20Institute%20for%20Disease%20Modeling%20with%20Bill%20Gates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20introductory%20letter%20published%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bfriends%26quot%3B%20part%20of%20the%20book%2C%20Myhrvold%20wrote%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bagonized%20long%20and%20hard%20about%20what%20to%20write.%26quot%3B%20He%20wrote%20that%20he%20decided%20to%20eschew%20the%20%26quot%3Bphilosophical%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bsilly%20and%20salacious.%26quot%3B%20Instead%2C%20he%20included%20a%20series%20of%20photos%20that%20he%20said%20he%20took%20on%20a%20trip%20to%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20seemed%20more%20appropriate%20than%20anything%20I%20could%20put%20in%20words%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wildlife%20photos%20depict%20animals%20in%20various%20suggestive%20ways%2C%20including%20a%20pair%20of%20lions%20mating%2C%20a%20zebra%20with%20a%20large%20penis%2C%20and%20a%20monkey%20with%20an%20erection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20Mhyrvold%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%20A%20spokesman%20previously%20told%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20that%20Mhyrvoid%20didn't%20recall%20the%20submission%20and%20%26quot%3Bregularly%20shares%20photos%20of%20and%20writes%20about%20animal%20behavior.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22933%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Male%20lion%20on%20top%20of%20female%20lion%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F