%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-guide-prompt-engineering-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eproper%20AI%20prompting%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20suggest%20using%20ChatGPT%20because%20it%20still%20has%20the%20largest%20market%20share%20compared%20to%20other%20AI%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20good%20prompt%20uses%20precise%20language%20and%20clear%20communication%20to%20explain%20a%20task%20and%20give%20it%20context.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-use-get-better-chatgpt-ai-prompt-guide%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPrompting%20is%20a%20conversation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20should%20be%20floating%20and%20dynamic%2C%20not%20just%20following%20a%20technical%20process%20like%20you're%20checking%20boxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20advice%20is%20to%20talk%20to%20AI%20like%20you%20would%20talk%20to%20a%20new%20hire.%20Just%20as%20you%20wouldn't%20assume%20a%20new%20hire%20knows%20your%20criteria%20for%20success%20or%20your%20reasoning%20for%20needing%20a%20certain%20task%20done%2C%20you%20can't%20expect%20AI%20to%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c110e4c8-c344-4098-b4fb-dd5480f840d5%5C%22%3EUse%20AI%20to%20create%20templates%20and%20workflow%20systems%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20can%20simplify%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-tools-changing-content-creators-work-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econtent%20creation%20process%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20whether%20you're%20drafting%20emails%2C%20creating%20social%20media%20posts%2C%20or%20editing%20a%20newsletter%2C%20as%20long%20as%20you%20make%20it%20repeatable.%20For%20content%20writing%2C%20I%20prefer%20to%20use%20Gemini%20for%20its%20creativity%20or%20Claud%20for%20its%20human-sounding%2C%20empathetic%20%26quot%3Bpersonality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20asking%20AI%20to%20draft%20me%20a%20one-off%20YouTube%20video%20script%2C%20I%20ask%20it%20to%20create%20a%20project%20that%20will%20act%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsc%2Fhow-to-win-the-ai-long-game%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereusable%20template%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20all%20future%20video%20scripts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20feed%20the%20AI%20as%20much%20important%20context%20and%20information%20as%20possible%2C%20such%20as%20my%20tone%20of%20voice%2C%20a%20style%20guide%2C%20field%20examples%2C%20or%20even%20a%20template%20knowledge%20file.%20I%20can%20even%20set%20up%20a%20command%20so%20that%20whenever%20I%20type%20in%20a%20word%20like%20%26quot%3BYouTube%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20knows%20to%20trigger%20the%20workflow%20and%20write%20a%20script.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20think%20about%20AI%20in%20terms%20of%20isolated%20features%20and%20tools%3B%20think%20about%20how%20you%20can%20combine%20the%20features%20to%20create%20a%20system%20and%20trigger%20a%20workflow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2281934c50-c4a7-4729-8493-6316bb467e87%5C%22%3EThere%20are%20a%20few%20ways%20AI%20can%20help%20with%20data%20analysis%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20tools%20can%20help%20structure%20data%2C%20enrich%20the%20context%2C%20and%20give%20important%20insights.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-gemini-bard%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI%20prefer%20Gemini%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20specifically%20its%20paid%20pro%20version%2C%20because%20it%20can%20handle%20large%20data%20sets%20with%20multiple%20rows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsk%20Gemini%20to%20%26quot%3Bclean%20up%26quot%3B%20or%20organize%20data%20by%20extracting%20rows%20that%20match%20certain%20criteria%2C%20and%20ask%20it%20to%20reference%20data%20from%20another%20dataset%20to%20create%20a%20new%20dataset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20submit%20large%20datasets%20to%20AI%20and%20ask%20it%20to%20summarize%20the%20data%20and%20generate%20insights.%20I%20might%20even%20ask%20it%20to%20build%20a%20beautiful%20dashboard%20that%20is%20ready%20to%20share%20with%20my%20team%20or%20stakeholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ac0291f8-64d6-4bd7-b90a-b78960c64134%5C%22%3EThere%20are%20cons%20to%20using%20AI%2C%20but%20it%20can%20be%20helpful%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20AI's%20biggest%20cons%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fartificial-intelligence-data-privacy-on-premises-information-technology-solutions-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edata%20privacy%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Employees%20may%20unintentionally%20pass%20sensitive%20data%20to%20AI%2C%20so%20companies%20must%20have%20clear%20guidelines%20around%20AI%20usage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20reality%20of%20AI%20is%20that%20it's%20replacing%20entry-level%20jobs.%20Leaders%20must%20make%20sure%20to%20upskill%20their%20more%20junior%20workforce%20and%20not%20overly%20automate%20entry-level%20roles%20for%20short-term%20wins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20so%20much%20collective%20anxiety%20about%20AI%20replacing%20humans%2C%20but%20I%20like%20to%20remind%20people%20that%20AI%20can%20never%20replace%20your%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20can%20help%20you%20learn%20faster%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20about%20taking%20shortcuts.%20Your%20biggest%20tool%20is%20still%20your%20judgment%2C%20which%20is%20derived%20from%20years%20of%20experience%2C%20trial%20and%20error%2C%20and%20critical%20thinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20how%20you've%20used%20AI%20to%20transform%20your%20career%20or%20life%3F%20If%20so%2C%20please%20reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20tmartinelli%40businessinsider.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstrategist-shares-how-to-use-ai-tools-chatgpt-gemini-claud-2025-09%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757409061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68bf1c0132af4d666ef77752%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstrategist-shares-how-to-use-ai-tools-chatgpt-gemini-claud-2025-09%22%2C%22summ