3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20creating%20a%20carve-out%20for%20search%2C%20we've%20focused%20in%20on%20this%20question%3A%20Does%20it%20reasonably%20lead%20to%20someone%20to%20visit%20the%20original%20location%20of%20the%20content%3F%26quot%3B%20Thomson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20recent%20interview.%C2%A0%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20think%20we're%20starting%20to%20come%20around%20to%20the%20view%20that%20that's%20a%20better%20framework%20overall.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%20that%20this%20would%20specifically%20rule%20out%20Google's%20AI%20Overviews.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20producing%20a%20summary%20that%20is%20not%20intended%20to%20direct%20people%20to%20the%20original%20source%20of%20the%20content%2C%20then%20that's%20off%20limits%2C%26quot%3B%20Thomson%20explained.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20not%20providing%20a%20search%20application%2C%20you're%20providing%20something%20else.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225bff697c-f91d-45fb-9781-e52c2fd3c28b%5C%22%3EIntense%20debate%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECooper%20went%20further%20by%20saying%20that%20AI%20answer%20engines%20are%20not%20a%20natural%20evolution%20of%20search%20engines.%20Instead%2C%20they%20are%20the%20result%20of%20intentional%20product%20choices%20made%20by%20Google%20and%20other%20Big%20Tech%20and%20AI%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20tech%20company%20crawls%20and%20indexes%20content%20and%20sends%20traffic%20to%20the%20origin%20of%20that%20information.%20This%20has%20been%20the%20experience%20for%20two%20decades%2C%26quot%3B%20Cooper%20explained.%20%26quot%3BTo%20come%20along%20now%20and%20say%20'we've%20made%20a%20product%20choice%20that%20replaces%20that%20and%20conflates%20two%20different%20things'%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20not%20the%20same.%20It's%20not%20delivering%20the%20same%20product%20experience%20for%20users%20or%20providers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20inside%20the%20IETF%20got%20particularly%20tense%20when%20publishers%20and%20others%20pressed%20their%20case%20to%20have%20the%20ability%20block%20AI%20bot%20crawlers%20while%20still%20allowing%20traditional%20search%20bots%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20traffic%20they%20bring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20some%20conflation%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Bradley%20Silver%2C%20global%20head%20of%20public%20policy%2C%20AI%20%26amp%3B%20IP%20at%20Advance%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20Cond%C3%A9%20Nast%20and%20a%20major%20shareholder%20of%20Reddit%20and%20Warner%20Bros.%20Discover.%20%26quot%3BThe%20use%20of%20AI%20to%20rank%20and%20re-rank%20organic%20search%20results%20should%20be%20distinguished%20from%20the%20use%20of%20generative%20AI%20to%20produce%20search%20results%20which%20aggregate%20and%20summarize%20the%20indexed%20content.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20this%20conflation%20is%20being%20driven%20by%20the%20need%20to%20compete%20with%20emerging%20AI%20answer%20engines%2C%20and%20argued%20this%20ignores%20creators'%20and%20publishers'%20wishes%20and%20is%20%26quot%3Bcausing%20real%20harm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChristopher%C2%A0Flammang%2C%20from%C2%A0publishing%20giant%20Elsevier%2C%20summed%20up%20those%20wishes%20forcefully%20in%20an%20email%20to%20the%20ITEF%20working%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20there%20is%20no%20effective%20mechanism%20for%20those%20who%20produce%20intellectual%20and%20creative%20content%20to%20say%3A%20'yes%2C%20I%20want%20to%20be%20found%20through%20search%3B%20no%2C%20I%20do%20not%20want%20to%20be%20summarized%20or%20rewritten%20by%20an%20AI%20system%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20early%20August.%20%26quot%3BWithout%20that%20line%2C%20we%20blur%20two%20fundamentally%20different%20uses%3A%20pointing%20to%20content%20(as%20search%20has%20historically%20done)%20and%20substituting%20for%20it%20(as%20AI%20summaries%20increasingly%20do).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ade54067-e817-427f-bbe7-adf89bc51009%5C%22%3EA%20change%20pushed%20through%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20early%20September%2C%20pres