20Golf%20courses%20and%20clubs%20are%20capitalizing%20on%20the%20links%20revival%20in%20a%20number%20of%20ways%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20most%20profitable%20is%20their%20merch.%20They%20know%20some%20of%20their%20logos%20are%20a%20hot%20commodity%20among%20those%20in%20the%20know%2C%20and%20the%20more%20exclusive%2C%20the%20better.%20They're%20catering%20to%20golfers%20who%20are%20seeking%20a%20lovely%2018-hole%20day%20%3Cem%3Eand%20%3C%2Fem%3Elooking%20to%20grab%20a%20collectible%20or%2010%20to%20commemorate%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20little%20trophy%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Greg%20Nathan%2C%20the%20president%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20National%20Golf%20Foundation%2C%20a%20trade%20association%20for%20the%20golf%20business.%20And%20a%20lucrative%20one%20at%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-you-should-never-do-golf-course-employees-pga-pros%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20golf%20course's%20pro%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20person%20who%20manages%20much%20of%20the%20facility%20and%20provides%20lessons%20%E2%80%94%20typically%20owned%20and%20ran%20its%20retail%20operation%2C%20hence%20calling%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bpro%20shop.%26quot%3B%20Revenue%20from%20the%20store%20was%20part%20of%20the%20pro's%20compensation.%20From%20the%20mid-1980s%20to%20the%20mid-2000s%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20golf%20courses%20were%20built%20around%20the%20US%2C%20and%20the%20market%20became%20oversupplied%20by%20the%20time%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-money-financial-economic-trauma-recession-student-debt-inflation-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGreat%20Recession%3C%2Fa%3E%20hit%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20economic%20turmoil.%20So%20some%20clubs%20went%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20make%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20decades%2C%20courses%20have%20taken%20over%20the%20pro%20shops%20themselves%20and%20brought%20in%20retail%20professionals%20to%20handle%20the%20business%20of%20selling%20their%20stuff.%20Even%20clubs%20that%20weren't%20hurting%20picked%20up%20on%20how%20lucrative%20the%20business%20is.%20The%20Association%20of%20Golf%20Merchandisers%20estimates%20golf%20shops%20generate%20annual%20sales%20of%20over%20%241%20billion%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20with%20everything%20being%20so%20much%20driven%20by%20online%20shopping%2C%20having%20a%20physical%20shop%20at%20a%20club%2C%20I%20think%2C%20still%20provides%20that%20hands-on%2C%20touchy-feely%20experience%20that%20people%20enjoy%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Patrick%20Casey%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Association%20of%20Golf%20Merchandisers%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20Casey's%20Club%20Consulting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERetail%20operations%20aren't%20the%20end-all%2C%20be-all%20of%20golf%20club%20revenue.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-expensive-golf-clubs-courses-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMembership%20dues%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20daily%20fees%2C%20food%2C%20beverage%2C%20and%20cart%20fees%20all%20rank%20above%20it%2C%20says%20Jeffrey%20Davis%2C%20the%20managing%20director%20of%20Fairway%20Advisors%2C%20a%20golf%20course%20brokerage%20and%20advisory%20firm.%20But%20it%20doesn't%20mean%20they're%20not%20important%2C%20from%20a%20sales%20perspective%20and%20a%20marketing%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20that%20are%20building%20new%20courses%20today%20are%20cognizant%20of%20their%20logo%20and%20the%20impact%20it%20would%20have%20on%20spreading%20the%20word%20about%20the%20club%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20For%20clubs%20and%20courses%20that%20don't%20put%20time%20and%20energy%20into%20merchandise%2C%20it%20can%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bmissed%20opportunity.%26quot%3B%20And%20some%20clubs%20that%20have%20changed%20logos%20have%20gone%20back%20to%20their%20original%20ones%2C%20to%20reclaim%20some%20historical%20mystique.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20more%20courses%20get%20in%20on%20the%20merch%20game%2C%20gear%20from%20all%20of%20them%20is%20not%20created%20equal.%20There%20are%20some%2016%2C000%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fgolf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egolf%20courses%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20the%20real%20juice%2C%20clout-wise%2C%20is%20with%20the%20top%20500%20or%20so%20private%20clubs%20and%20resorts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20500%20courses%2C%20they%20do%20some%20very%20serious%20revenue%20because%20it's%20very%20logo-driven%2C%26quot%3B%20Nathan%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20golf%20courses%20renovate%20%E2%80%94%20as%20many%20of%20them%20are%20doing%20right%20now%20%E2%80%94%20they%20often%20look%20at%20the%20internal%20facilities%2C%20too%2C%20including%20their%20shops.%20A%20well-appointed%20shop%20is%20a%20place%20for%20members%20at%20private%20clubs%20to%20pick%20up%20gear%20for%20themselves%20(often%20at%20a%20friendly%20price)%20and%20show%20off%20to%20their%20guests%2C%20who%20can%20also%20pick%20up%20stuff%20(at%20a%20not-as-friendly%20price).%20The%20markups%20on%20branded%20items%20and%20general%20gear%20can%20be%20quite%20large%2C%20given%20how%20exclusive%20the%20logos%20are%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20customer%20is%20a%20little%20trapped.%20If%20you%20forgot%20golf%20balls%20for%20the%20day%2C%20the%20ones%20at%20the%20course%20are%20going%20to%20cost%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20logo%20collecting%20has%20become%20more%20of%20a%20thing%20among%20golfers%2C%20clubs%20are%20figuring%20out%20new%20ways%20to%20capitalize.%20For%20example%2C%20some%20are%20leaning%20into%20e-commerce%20so%20that%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20stock%20all%20of%20their%20merchandise%2C%20and%20if%20people%20come%20to%20play%20for%20a%20day%20and%20don't%20have%20time%20for%20shopping%2C%20they%20can%20pick%20up%20gear%20online.%20(This%20may%20open%20up%20some%20breaches%20of%20the%20unwritten%20rule%20that%20people%20can't%20wear%20logos%20of%20courses%20they%20haven't%20played%2C%20but%20we'll%20leave%20that%20for%20another%20day.)%20For%20the%20courses%20and%20clubs%20that%20do%20merch%20right%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20like%20found%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Davis%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20positive%20time%20for%20the%20golf%20industry%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Nathan%20says.%20Logo-mania%20is%20part%20of%20it.%20The%20more%20popular%20the%20sport%20becomes%2C%20the%20more%20the%20merch%20matters%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20for%20those%20in%20the%20know.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20going%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-disney-world-souvenirs-worth-it-former-cast-member%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDisney%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20get%20some%20souvenirs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Femily-stewart%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEmily%20Stewart%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%2C%20writing%20about%20business%20and%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgolf-clubs-merch-hype-logo-collecting-sports-revival-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757405041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68bb336857d362d375e7a46a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgolf-clubs-merch-hype-logo-collecting-sports-revival-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Golf%20clubs%20are%20leveraging%20merch%20hype%20and%20transforming%20logos%20into%20collectible%20trophies.%20It's%20driving%20even%20more%20revenue%20for%20the%2