%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20largest%20since%20the%20war%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20photos%20of%20the%20site%20show%20what%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20remains%20of%20the%20missile%20in%20a%20battered%20but%20structurally%20intact%20room%2C%20indicating%20that%20its%20warhead%20didn't%20trigger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20unclear%20what%20payload%20the%20missile%20was%20carrying%2C%20the%20incident%20could%20signal%20a%20reliability%20issue%20with%20one%20of%20Russia's%20advanced%20precision%20weapons.%20However%2C%20such%20failures%20can%20happen%20with%20missiles%20in%20wartime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKatarina%20Mathernova%2C%20the%20European%20Union's%20ambassador%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20posted%20the%20images%20to%20social%20media%20on%20Monday%20after%20visiting%20the%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20photos%20captured%20a%20large%2C%20round%20piece%20of%20wrecked%20metal%20with%20turbine%20blades%2C%20closely%20resembling%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-long-range-palianytsia-rocket-drone-hybrid-russia-war-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eturbojet%20or%20turbofan%20engine%3C%2Fa%3E%20used%20by%20Russia's%20cruise%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20piece%20of%20the%20debris%20was%20labeled%20in%20Cyrillic%20as%20%26quot%3BFilter%20FT-1%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20reported%20component%20of%20the%20TRDD-50%20engine%20that's%20known%20to%20power%20the%20Russian%20Iskander-K%20missile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wreckage%20of%20a%20turbojet%20for%20a%20cruise%20missile%20is%20seen%20in%20a%20structurally%20intact%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68bfafc532af4d666ef781a7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20photo%20posted%20by%20Mathernova%20shows%20the%20apparent%20remains%20of%20an%20Iskander-K%20cruise%20missile.%3Cp%3EFacebook%2FKatarina%20Mathernova%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20photos%20also%20showed%20a%20breached%20wall%20in%20the%20Cabinet%20building%20where%20the%20missile%20likely%20entered%2C%20along%20with%20the%20charred%20remains%20of%20parts%20of%20the%20headquarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20internal%20damage%20likely%20stemmed%20from%20a%20fire%20that%20Ukrainian%20authorities%20said%20broke%20out%20after%20the%20missile%20hit%20the%20building.%20Local%20media%20reported%20that%20the%20missile's%20fuel%20tanks%20started%20the%20blaze.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Officials%20and%20staff%20in%20hardhats%20observe%20the%20remains%20of%20Ukraine's%20Cabinet%20headquarters'%20upper%20floors.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68bfba7932af4d666ef781f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMathernova's%20photo%20appears%20to%20show%20the%20point%20where%20the%20Russian%20missile%20breached%20the%20building.%3Cp%3EFacebook%2FKatarina%20Mathernova%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20apart%20from%20its%20scorched%20interior%2C%20the%20Cabinet%20building%20remained%20mostly%20structurally%20intact.%20Ground-launched%20Iskander-K%20missiles%20generally%20carry%20warheads%20with%20a%20mass%20of%20450%20to%20500%20kg%2C%20or%20990%20to%201%2C100%20pounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnly%20thanks%20to%20the%20missile%20failing%20to%20fully%20detonate%2C%20the%20entire%20building%20was%20not%20reduced%20to%20rubble%2C%26quot%3B%20Mathernova%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20thanks%20to%20the%20rapid%20action%20of%20Ukraine's%20amazing%20rescue%20services%20%E2%80%94%20true%20heroes%20%E2%80%94%20the%20fire%20was%20contained%20to%20the%20three%20floors%2C%20before%20it%20would%20swallow%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20building.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fpost.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Fkmathernova%252Fposts%252Fpfbid02Bn6E1Nvp1Fiu9opiP9nKvzk8cJXca89hJ8RnqUrVPsi54HEtd2MneB4tiFfoP8C3l%26show_text%3Dtrue%26width%3D500%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22710%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EEuropean%20and%20Ukrainian%20officials%20have%20condemned%20the%20missile%20strike%20on%20the%20Cabinet%20building%20as%20a%20sign%20that%20Russia%20continues%20to%20act%20in%20bad%20faith%20despite%20courting%20ceasefire%20talks%20with%20the%20US.%20The%20Iskander-K's%20missile%20variants%2C%20the%209M728%20and%20the%20newer%209M729%2C%20are%20precision-guided%20munitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20evidence%20of%20this%20existential%20battle%20is%20right%20in%20front%20of%20us%3A%20Putin%20is%20deliberately%20targeting%20the%20country's%20lifelines%20%E2%80%94%20its%20government%2C%20its%20energy%2C%20its%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Mathernova%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndriy%20Yermak%2C%20chief%20of%20staff%20for%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FAndriyYermak%2Fstatus%2F1965100984897802341%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20on%20Monday%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20had%20spoken%20to%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%20about%20the%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20strikes%20kill%20civilians%2C%20including%20children%2C%20and%20destroy%20our%20infrastructure%2C%26quot%3B%20Yermak%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BFor%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%20enemy%20attacked%20the%20building%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20Ukraine%20%E2%80%94%20Iskander%20missile%20strike.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20air%20command%20said%20the%20Iskander-K%20missile%20was%20one%20of%20nine%20cruise%20missiles%20launched%20by%20Russia%20on%20Sunday%2C%20as%20part%20of%20a%20massive%20wave%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-war-interceptor-drone-150-russian-shahed-gerbera-zelenskyy-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elong-range%20exploding%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20decoys.%20Kyiv%20said%20its%20air%20force%20detected%20at%20least%20810%20drones%20that%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20regularly%20attacked%20Ukrainian%20cities%20with%20its%20Iskander%20launchers%2C%20and%20is%20often%20accused%20of%20using%20them%20to%20target%20infrastructure%20and%20civilian%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202023%2C%20one%20of%20its%20most%20high-profile%20strikes%20with%20the%20launcher%20involved%20a%20hit%20with%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvideo-shocking-moment-russian-iskander-missile-slams-into-chernihiv-theatre-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIskander-M%20ballistic%20missile%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20killed%20seven%20people%20at%20a%20landmark%20drama%20theater%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Chernihiv.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-iskander-missile-hit-ukraine-cabinet-building-warhead-didnt-detonate-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757401133000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68bfb98b32af4d666ef781f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-iskander-missile-hit-ukraine-cabinet-building-warhead-didnt-detonate-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20photo%20captured%20a%20turbojet%20or%20turbofan%20engine%20for%20the%20Russian%20Iskander-K%20in%20a%20mostly%20intact%20room%2C%20indicating%20that%20its%20warhead%20failed%20to%20explode.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A82%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-iskander-missile-hit-ukraine-cabinet-building-warhead-didnt-detonate-2025-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%2